Please paste the code as written below in the HTML source code of PDF editor:

<div class="first_name" data-field_value="{{8e09-ecc4-137f}}">
<h3>Name :</h3>
{{8e09-ecc4-137f}}</div>
Here "8e09-ecc4-137f" is component-Id of fields whose value you would like to show or hide based on condition.

Please paste the code as written below in the PDF Javascript(Advanced Settings) of PDF editor:

<script type="text/javascript" src="https://d3iyvxaud7i110.cloudfront.net/vendor/jquery/jquery-2.1.3.min.js"></script>
<script>
(function(){
    //Based on value  , hide and show section
  if (!$(".first_name").attr("data-field_value") ) {
   $(".first_name").attr("style","display:none;");
  }
})();
</script>
